<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think she's really worried.</b></font>

192
00:11:51,777 --> 00:11:54,617
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huaze Lei, talk to Daoming Si.</b></font>

193
00:11:54,977 --> 00:11:59,297
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tell him to treat Xiaozi better
