212
00:12:49,617 --> 00:12:50,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si.</b></font>

213
00:12:52,657 --> 00:12:53,497
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

214
00:12:56,297 --> 00:12:57,817
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't I tell you not to come here?</b></font>

215
00:12:57,897 --> 00:12:59,977
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm really going to be mad
if you're so unreasonable.</b></font>

216
00:13:01,897 --> 00:13:04,377
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why can't I come here?
