217
00:13:05,097 --> 00:13:06,857
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can't you be nicer to me?</b></font>

218
00:13:07,897 --> 00:13:09,617
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She doesn't seem like Si's girlfriend.</b></font>

219
00:13:10,497 --> 00:13:12,257
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think they're having an argument.</b></font>

220
00:13:12,337 --> 00:13:13,937
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's not stay here.</b></font>

221
00:13:14,497 --> 00:13:15,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you want me to do?</b></font>

222
00:13:16,617 --> 00:13:17,497
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want you to kiss me.</b></font>

223
00:13:19,257 --> 00:13:20,297
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Kiss me now.</b></font>

224
00:13:21,857 --> 00:13:22,737
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

225
00:13:23,857 --> 00:13:24,897
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you still like Shancai?</b></font>

226
00:13:26,057 --> 00:13:28,457
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're always deep in thought
