229
00:13:33,977 --> 00:13:35,297
<font color="#ffff00"><b>feel insecure.</b></font>

230
00:13:45,097 --> 00:13:46,097
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want proof.</b></font>

231
00:13:46,737 --> 00:13:49,657
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you don't like Shancai, then kiss me.</b></font>

232
00:13:57,697 --> 00:13:58,657
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Close your eyes.</b></font>

233
00:14:52,577 --> 00:14:54,537
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't you want Si to be nicer to Xiaozi?</b></font>

234
00:14:54,617 --> 00:14:56,097
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't need to be worried now.</b></font>

235
00:14:58,937 --> 00:15:00,137
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you so quiet?</b></font>

236
00:15:01,497 --> 00:15:03,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you feel upset?</b></font>

237
00:15:04,697 --> 00:15:07,097
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Upset? Who's upset?</b></font>

238
00:15:07,897 --> 00:15:10,457
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think this is good.
That's what I hoped would happen.</b></font>

239
00:15:11,417 --> 00:15:12,977
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I feel like I'm having</b></font>

240
00:15:13,057 --> 00:15:15,977
<font color="#ffff00"><b>vacations for New Year, summer,
and winter all together.</b></font>

241
00:15:16,337 --> 00:15:17,297
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

242
00:15:17,577 --> 00:15:19,497
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's not enough to describe
my excitement.</b></font>

243
00:15:20,337 --> 00:15:22,257
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I should say I'm as ecstatic</b></font>

244
00:15:22,337 --> 00:15:25,017
<font color="#ffff00"><b>as when my mom sold a year's worth
