245
00:15:26,257 --> 00:15:27,497
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm so happy I'm crying.</b></font>

246
00:15:28,817 --> 00:15:30,857
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Really?
-Why?</b></font>

247
00:15:31,937 --> 00:15:35,097
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You blab nonstop whenever someone
guesses what you're thinking.</b></font>

248
00:15:36,217 --> 00:15:37,377
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't.</b></font>

249
00:15:38,097 --> 00:15:40,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't act like
you're a psychologist, okay?</b></font>

250
00:15:42,857 --> 00:15:44,657
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It'd be great if you're that focused
in class.</b></font>

251
00:15:45,097 --> 00:15:45,937
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

252
00:15:47,017 --> 00:15:47,897
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your bag.</b></font>

253
00:15:57,257 --> 00:15:59,617
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>You kissed her when she asked you to.
