331
00:19:40,657 --> 00:19:41,977
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A straight nose and a wide mouth.</b></font>

332
00:19:54,417 --> 00:19:55,417
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What a coincidence.</b></font>

333
00:19:55,697 --> 00:19:57,137
