<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, I'm not mad anymore.</b></font>

336
00:20:07,257 --> 00:20:08,417
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I'm warning you.</b></font>

337
00:20:08,937 --> 00:20:10,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't judge me again.</b></font>

338
00:20:17,137 --> 00:20:18,977
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's cold. You should wear
