339
00:20:20,377 --> 00:20:21,657
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you still have class later?</b></font>

340
00:20:22,417 --> 00:20:23,657
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. I'm done for the day.</b></font>

341
00:20:28,937 --> 00:20:30,257
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is for you.</b></font>

342
00:20:39,817 --> 00:20:40,697
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's the matter?</b></font>

343
00:20:41,977 --> 00:20:42,937
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Nothing.</b></font>

344
00:20:43,777 --> 00:20:46,257
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just feel that it's so cold outside.</b></font>

345
00:20:47,137 --> 00:20:50,017
