348
00:20:56,697 --> 00:20:58,137
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You've never mentioned that before.</b></font>

349
00:21:03,417 --> 00:21:04,337
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai is over there.</b></font>

350
00:21:11,617 --> 00:21:12,497
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

351
00:21:12,577 --> 00:21:13,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on.</b></font>

352
00:21:17,137 --> 00:21:19,537
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, can we join you?</b></font>

353
00:21:20,097 --> 00:21:21,657
