<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, we're not...</b></font>

355
00:21:23,777 --> 00:21:25,017
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is Huaze Lei.</b></font>

356
00:21:25,097 --> 00:21:26,217
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We just met coincidentally.</b></font>

357
00:21:26,777 --> 00:21:27,897
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's Huaze Lei?</b></font>

358
00:21:28,617 --> 00:21:29,577
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come here.</b></font>

359
00:21:31,697 --> 00:21:32,817
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hi.</b></font>

360
00:21:32,897 --> 00:21:35,057
