<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.</b></font>

382
00:22:31,337 --> 00:22:32,777
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai thinks so too.</b></font>

383
00:22:35,257 --> 00:22:38,817
<font color="#ffff00"><b>By the way, we have a nice resort hotel
