<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ma'am.</b></font>

395
00:23:16,057 --> 00:23:17,377
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Any new developments?</b></font>

396
00:23:18,817 --> 00:23:22,777
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si and Xiaozi will go to the He Group's
